info.name: /lolprofile
info.description: Display a profile of a League of Legends player. The profile has informations such as: ranks, winrate, top mastery, etc...
examples: /lolprofile BR1 badda bing - Display the profile of the player `badda bing` in the `Brazilian` server.
/lolprofile KR Faker - Display the profile of the player `Faker` in the `Korean` server.
